desc:
Called when an animation is looping and starts a subsequent loop. A looping
animation (repeat=3) will undergo a life cycle like this:
onAnimationStart  -&gt;
onAnimationLoop   -&gt;
onAnimationLoop   -&gt;
onAnimationEnd    !
A looping ping-pong animation (repeat=3) will look like this:
onAnimationStart  -&gt;
onAnimationLoop   &lt;-
onAnimationLoop   -&gt;
onAnimationEnd    !
